ers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"This provider should be integrated as a ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllTextAreaComponentTokensProvider"},{"text":" implementation inside ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"text":" implementation to use.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Custom themes can use subclass of ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProvider"},{"text":" and apply the provider they need.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It implements also the protocol ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"TextAreaComponentTokens"},{"text":" so as to expose the component tokens for ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"text area"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" through any ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Text area"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" components tokens are defined with semantic tokens of sizes (from ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSizeSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":")"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and spaces (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider"},{"text":").","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProvider","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProvider"}],"type":"topic","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange